# Screen & component purity

- No `type` / `interface` / `enum` in screens or components — use `src/types/*`.
- No reusable helpers in screens/components — put in `src/utils/*` and export via `src/utils/index.ts`.
- No API calls, effects, or orchestration in screens — use `use*Controller` hooks + contexts.
- Booking flow math/payloads → `useBookingFlowController` + `src/utils/booking-flow.ts`.

Full guide: `docs/architecture/screen-purity.md`
